Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://hifiberry.com/os

Package: hifiberry-baseconfig
Architecture: all
Depends: uuid
Description: HiFiBerry base configuration script
 This package provides the base configuration script for HiFiBerry OS.
 It ensures that a unique UUID is generated and stored for the system
 if one does not already exist.
 .
 The script generates a UUID in /etc/uuid if the file is missing or empty,
 which is used for system identification purposes.
